description: This mobile gourmet cupcake shop is bringing pure deliciousness right to you and delivering smiles all over town! With red velvet, rosewater, french vanilla, chocolate cherry, and much more, Dolce's range of delicious flavors never fails to impress, and with gluten-free options, anyone can indulge their sweet tooth without fear. Stop by, and get some of the best cupcakes in Dade, Broward, and Palm Beach County!
name: Dolce Gourmet Cupcakes
